{"tid":1531183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【*轉* 何大學生被校方威嚇】","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:48:58.000Z","uid":286839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f62bff2e78daa7951d7fd817ceaa1fc335b6e637","tid":1531183,"uid":286839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"【*轉* 何大學生被校方威嚇】<br />\n<br />\n孔教學院大成何郭佩珍中學100名學生「被安排」於學校內的一個房間，禁止離開<br />\n<br />\n校方威脅將罷課學生名單上繳給教育局🈹<br />\n<br />\n疑似校方人員對話：<br />\n👹「呢個唔係你嘅自由」<br />\n👹「你哋從來都冇呢個自由，點解會覺得自己有呢？」<br />\n👹「如果你要有自由嘅，唯一就係唔好做呢度嘅學生」<br />\n👹「罷課只係一種表態，同發聲係兩回事」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n中學生校外集會<br />\n日期：2/9<br />\n時間：1030-1700<br />\n地點：中環愛丁堡廣場（近大會堂）<br />\nDress code：校服<br />\n<br />\n#着校服<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10162368568270230?sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100375550229%2Fposts%2F10162368568270230%3Fsfns%3Dxmo&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR28%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=31d61750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10162368568270230?sfns=xmo</a>"}]}